T02TD2912E:311b-1: badzra bi d'a ra na mandal bi dhi:/
T02TD2912E:311b-3: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga /
T02TD2912E:311b-4: dpal rdo rje rnam par 'jo mas pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2912E:311b-5: gdug pa 'dul mdzad khro bo che //
T02TD2912E:311b-6: rdo rje can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2912E:311b-7: gang gis legs par smin byed pa'i //
T02TD2912E:311b-8: 'khor lo'i cho ga bshad par bya //
T02TD2912E:311b-9: slob dpon mtshan nyid bzang ldan pas //
T02TD2912E:311b-10: legs par brtags pa'i slob ma la //
T02TD2912E:311b-11: tshul bzhin bsnyen pa sngon song nas //
T02TD2912E:311b-12: ri bo bzang sogs shis pa'i sar //
T02TD2912E:311b-13: bslang dang sbyang dang gzung ba dang //
T02TD2912E:311b-14: bsrung ba'i cho ga legs byas pas //
T02TD2912E:311b-15: thog mar bum pa'i bya ba las //
T02TD2912E:311b-16: gser ram dngul lam yang na zangs //
T02TD2912E:311b-17: kham las gnyis lnga nyi shu lnga //
T02TD2912E:311b-18: dkar po'i rdzas kyis legs byugs la //
T02TD2912E:311b-19: rang lha'i mtshan ma ldan par bya //
T02TD2912E:311b-20: ma nyams ras kyis mgul dkris pa //
T02TD2912E:311b-21: dri zhim chu yis bkang ba dang //
T02TD2912E:311b-22: 'bru sman rin chen lngar ldan pa //
T02TD2912E:311b-23: bzang po'i shing gis kha brgyan nas //
T02TD2912E:311b-24: ku sha'i stan la yang dag gzhag / lha yi 'khor lo bsgom pa dang//
T02TD2912E:312a-0: @312a * // bzlas mthar mchod zhu bdud rtsir bya //
T02TD2912E:312a-1: slob ma gsum la skyabs 'gro dang //
T02TD2912E:312a-2: byang chub tu ni sems bskyed pas //
T02TD2912E:312a-3: sgo gsum mi dge las bzlog cing //
T02TD2912E:312a-4: kun du spyod pa gtsang ldan pas //
T02TD2912E:312a-5: rang lha'i rnal 'byor brtson byed pa'i //
T02TD2912E:312a-6: dam tshig rjes su 'dzin pa la //
T02TD2912E:312a-7: gnas gsum yi ge gsum gyur pa'i //
T02TD2912E:312a-8: mtshan ma gsum gyis byin brlabs te //
T02TD2912E:312a-9: rdo rje dang bcas dris reg dang //
T02TD2912E:312a-10: mchod pa lnga yis legs mchod bya //
T02TD2912E:312a-11: dkyil 'khor byi dor legs byas par //
T02TD2912E:312a-12: dri dang me tog tshom bur bcas //
T02TD2912E:312a-13: bskyed dang gnyis med mchod pa la //
T02TD2912E:312a-14: bstod de nam mkhar gshegs gsol bya//
T02TD2912E:312a-15: dri dang ba yi lci ba yis //
T02TD2912E:312a-16: legs par byugs pa'i stegs bu la //
T02TD2912E:312a-17: gtsang ma'i ras kyi srad bu dang //
T02TD2912E:312a-18: man ngag rig pas thig btab ste //
T02TD2912E:312a-19: der ni kha dog lnga ldan pa'i //
T02TD2912E:312a-20: tshon gyis khro bo'i 'khor lo bri //
T02TD2912E:312a-21: gru bzhi kun nas sgo bzhi pa //
T02TD2912E:312a-22: tva ra na bzhis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD2912E:312a-23: phyi rol rdo rje'i phreng ba dang//
T02TD2912E:312a-24: 'bar ba'i phreng bas yongs su bskor //
T02TD2912E:312a-25: nang dbus rdo rje kha bzhi pa //
T02TD2912E:312a-27: der ni rang lha mtshan ma rnams //
T02TD2912E:312a-28: ji ltar mthong ba'i rjes 'brang bri //
T02TD2912E:312a-29: der yang bum pa dgod pa dang //
T02TD2912E:312a-30: bla re me tog phreng mdzes pas //
T02TD2912E:312a-31: sna tshogs mchod pa'i bkod par ldan //
T02TD2912E:312a-32: dri zhim bum pa gtor ma bcas //
T02TD2912E:312a-33: slob dpon kun spyod gtsang ldan pas //
T02TD2912E:312a-34: gtsang ma chu yis khrus byas te //
T02TD2912E:312a-35: sar pa'i gos dang rab ldan pas //
T02TD2912E:312a-36: bde ba'i stan la legs 'dug ste //
T02TD2912E:312a-37: mdun gnas 'khor lo gtod pa yis //
T02TD2912E:312a-38: rnam sbyang dam tshig bskyed pa dang //
T02TD2912E:312a-39: ye shes gnyis med byin rlabs dang //
T02TD2912E:312a-40: dbang bskur mchod dang bstod bzlas bya //
T02TD2912E:312a-41: dri zhim chu yis legs bkrus te //
T02TD2912E:312a-42: bzang po'i dri yis legs byugs shing //
T02TD2912E:312a-43: sar ba'i gos dang rgyan ldan pa'i //
T02TD2912E:312a-44: slob ma dkyil 'khor nang bcug ste //
T02TD2912E:312a-45: ku sha'i stan la legs bzhag nas //
T02TD2912E:312a-46: thog mar bum pa'i chus dbang bskur //
T02TD2912E:312a-47: rdo rjes dri yi thig le dang //
T02TD2912E:312a-48: mngon par bsngags pa'i me tog phreng //
T02TD2912E:312a-49: bkra shis tshigs bcad mgo la sbyin //
T02TD2912E:312a-50: bsgom dang bzlas dang gtad pa dang //
T02TD2912E:312a-51: sbyin bya bsgrub bya sku dang gsung //
T02TD2912E:312a-52: thugs dang yon tan phrin las la //
T02TD2912E:312a-54: mnan pa'i las la dbang bar bya //
T02TD2912E:312b-0: de nas mchod dang @312b gtor ma dang //
T02TD2912E:312b-2: tshul 'dis smin byas slob ma ni //
T02TD2912E:312b-3: las dang dngos grub kun dbang phyug / gzhan la phan byed bdag nyid che //
T02TD2912E:312b-4: lha rigs sngags rnams kun nong 'gyur //
T02TD2912E:312b-5: rdo rje khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du //
T02TD2912E:312b-6: slob ma yongs su smin byed pa'i //
T02TD2912E:312b-7: cho ga legs bkod bsod nams des //
T02TD2912E:312b-8: kun gyis bla med mchog thob shog / rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga bram ze dz'a ya warmas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
